author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
After over a decade, Adam finally meets the original prop that inspired his One Day Build of the Barbarella space rifle, as made famous by the 1968 LIFE magazine cover featuring Jane Fonda. Alongside this iconic prop are other recognizable pieces from the film, from hand crafted blasters to armored costumes that made the movie so memorable!

Learn more about this prop and see more details at: https://propstoreauction.com/auctions/info/id/462
Adam's Barbarella Space Rifle prop replica build: https://youtu.be/QWiqr-lwYA0

Shot by Josh Self and edited by Norman Chan
Music by Jinglepunks
